197
00:10:18.400 --> 00:10:21.730
Your lordship, though not cleanpast your youth,

198
00:10:21.730 --> 00:10:23.870
hath yet some smack of age inyou,

199
00:10:23.870 --> 00:10:26.370
some relish of the saltness oftime,

200
00:10:26.370 --> 00:10:28.570
and I must humbly beseech yourlordship

201
00:10:28.570 --> 00:10:31.000
