225
00:11:11.670 --> 00:11:15.430
Oh, very well, my lord; verywell.

226
00:11:15.430 --> 00:11:19.770
Rather, an't please you, it'sthe disease of not listening,

227
00:11:19.770 --> 00:11:23.770
