247
00:12:08.330 --> 00:12:10.730
But since all is well, keep itso.

248
00:12:10.730 --> 00:12:13.700
You follow the young prince upand down like his ill angel.

249
00:12:13.700 --> 00:12:14.700
Not so, my lord.

250
00:12:14.700 --> 00:12:16.300
You that are old consider not

251
00:12:16.300 --> 00:12:17.870
